Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.98,0:01:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看 那個人帥呆了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.75,0:01:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.85,0:01:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他是怎麼了？他不認識路嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像要去俱樂部呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.82,0:01:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去跟他搭訕吧 搞不好會找我們去玩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.33,0:01:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寒假結束了 第三學期也開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.17,0:01:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別老是一副不可一世的樣子行不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我要讓你從嘴巴吐出對不起這三個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.81,0:01:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.91,0:01:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣啦！臭小子 你真是不知羞恥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在店門口大吵大鬧才是不知羞恥吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得好 你這個娘娘腔 給我出來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就出來了啊 蠢貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.79,0:02:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 本田同學 辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.43,0:02:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.60,0:02:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個還是老樣子 感情還是那麼差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.73,0:02:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新年的時候我許的願是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.57,0:02:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「希望他們兩個能和睦相處」呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.77,0:02:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是一點效果都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你夠了吧 吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.01,0:02:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你用你的力量讓我閉嘴啊 你這個娘娘腔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}韭菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.08,0:02:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚啊啊啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.22,0:02:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.99,0:02:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下子應該會安分一點了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂—
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.59,0:02:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,澡盆的水已經放掉了 你要洗嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…今天不洗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？不會吧——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不洗澡…好髒喲～～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想把這個傢伙吊在屋頂上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔…好像感冒了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.94,0:03:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！那就糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點…發燒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感冒剛開始要好好調養才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.78,0:03:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃了藥之後早點去睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天最好還是請假比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 用不著那樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是明天有耐力賽跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 還有這種比賽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天寒地凍的 年輕人可真辛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼耐力賽跑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耐力賽跑馬拉松…跑一大段路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說…就是勝負的較量！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.94,0:03:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！明天我就讓你知道我們兩個誰比較快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可、可是…草摩同學他…好像感冒了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃個飯洗個澡就會好了！你休想逃避！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是說實在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要身體一虛弱的話就會很容易變身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以絕對不能逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.26,0:03:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好擔心哦…還是希望他能夠休息…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.94,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學…你還好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.04,0:04:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 應該沒什麼問題…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.95,0:04:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我請假的話 那個傢伙又會囉唆個沒完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.75,0:04:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 好像沒有看到魚谷同學呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.39,0:04:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像蹺課了 小花在那邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女生先跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到校門口的起跑點集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先過去囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.20,0:04:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小花 我們今天要連小魚的份一起加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.64,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…雖然我不擅長跑步 可是我會盡力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.31,0:04:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位 預備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小花!?妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 我已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑不動了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.42,0:04:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只能慢慢走而已了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.62,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心 我會慢慢走過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢走…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小花！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走要爬都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過花島至少也要就起跑點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小花 妳還好吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男生應該也已經就起跑位置了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學他…真的不要緊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.75,0:05:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白頭髮！老人!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.69,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好、好年輕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思 因為你的白頭髮太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我以為是老人倒在路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我弄錯了 真的很抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知不知道草摩家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.54,0:05:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要贏！我要打敗由希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.05,0:05:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害…那兩個跑好快哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.28,0:05:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是…一百公尺賽跑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你話中有話哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.59,0:06:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩…莫非你是草摩家的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 妳認識嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是的！初次見面 我是本田…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.22,0:06:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.97,0:06:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.84,0:06:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是草摩家的人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許也是十二生肖之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.85,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.65,0:06:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？阿夾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.69,0:06:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢伙 搞什麼東西！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好不容易才把由希甩開的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.66,0:06:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不這麼做的話 怎麼能把你擋下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿春…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種行為十分危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是發生在阿夾以外的人身上一定會受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以絕對不能模仿哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不能這麼做啦！喂！有沒有在聽我說話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.34,0:06:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次是阿春嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陸續來找我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用上學嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.68,0:07:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期天的時候我想出去走走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果不知不覺間迷了路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我發現的時候已經過了三天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷路別說得理直氣壯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.83,0:07:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子 路痴一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很樂天的迷路人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.70,0:07:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 這三天你都沒有洗澡囉 髒鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.34,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看我們還是先換個地方說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 他叫草摩潑春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小我們一歲 今年中學三年級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿春 她是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不敢當 請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潑春很有禮貌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來不像中學三年級 很穩重呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你來這裡做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.16,0:07:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來打架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.13,0:07:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過年的時候想找你挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你們不是沒有參加宴會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我來找你們 好了 來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.87,0:08:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等、等一下 我現在正在進行重要的比賽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是花了三天的時間呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你自己要迷路的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.68,0:08:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不清楚他們在講什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是不太好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.65,0:08:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.25,0:08:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就照阿春的話去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說不行就是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.19,0:08:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點滾回去 我現在可忙得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.27,0:08:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少在那邊囉哩八唆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是男子漢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是什麼較量都會奉陪的 小貓咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.51,0:08:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下地獄去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.21,0:08:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你到底有什麼深仇大恨 你要這樣來妨礙我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家都稱呼他是「黑春」呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑…黑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然阿春看起來有點迷糊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是只要他失控的話就完全不講道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以家族的人都叫他「黑春」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.63,0:09:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來他和樂羅是同一型囉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.04,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的個性比樂羅還要差勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.48,0:09:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不能在一旁看好戲 由希 你也要參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算參加又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 阿夾！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就站著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去戰鬥！戰鬥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.05,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本田同學 他們好像會扯很久 妳還是先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.83,0:09:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾 你什麼時候變得這麼拖泥帶水的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你黑春還真是一點都沒錯 你的個性真的很差勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.37,0:09:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆 要是你繼續拖拖拉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別怪我對那個小姐不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？怎麼個不客氣法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.77,0:09:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要這樣、那樣 再給她來個那樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼!?你這個混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.05,0:09:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記小時候你上廁所迷路我帶你去的那份恩情了嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個黑春真是一點也不可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.22,0:09:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰喚醒你體內的壞因子的？是我啊…不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事和這件事根本沒有瓜葛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你為什麼要把女生牽扯進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.59,0:09:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點關係都沒有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 一點關係都沒有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.79,0:10:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是男人的決鬥和女人沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是氣死人了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個死孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你能打倒我 隨便你打哪裡都沒關係！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打鼻子也沒關係嗎？膽小鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然敢這樣叫我 臭小鬼！\N本田同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.41,0:10:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你吃不完兜著走！\N他們真的會扯很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是先走吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.91,0:10:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可、可、可是…應該阻止他們才對…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.15,0:10:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 花島！妳好歹也跑一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.82,0:10:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 我要打到囉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 你已經被我看穿了你還不明白嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.63,0:10:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼變成格鬥動畫了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別理他們 本田同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想打就讓他們打好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.84,0:10:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我不想被卷進去遭受池魚之殃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.84,0:10:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要 死也不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.55,0:11:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是剛剛看到的潑春…是那麼成熟穩重啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.39,0:11:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什麼拳啊 太輕了啦 對我完全沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要他失控的話 整個人都會變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.00,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼草摩家的人看起來都是表裡不一的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你少囂張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.17,0:11:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和由希比起來 你只不過是隻鱉而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.94,0:11:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！連比我們晚學武術的由希你都打不贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還修行個屁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.55,0:11:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遜斃了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你連鱉都不如 只是綠烏龜！水龜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子！這次真的讓你下地獄！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.82,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真無聊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.76,0:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…看起來…好像阿夾比較厲害呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.80,0:11:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…如果和阿春比的話 是阿夾比較厲害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是格鬥狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.11,0:11:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前就很喜歡學習…武術呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.85,0:12:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…草摩同學…草摩同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.28,0:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.28,0:12:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.09,0:12:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發作了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 支氣管…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.36,0:12:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好燙啊 感冒的時候應該多注意一點才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.93,0:12:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先讓他躺在這裡吧 我馬上連絡本家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草摩同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.27,0:12:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像很痛苦…我應該勸他不要硬撐 多休息的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.38,0:12:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想回本家嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看這場較量暫時保留好了 阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.92,0:12:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 先到紫吳老師的家吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.22,0:12:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 耐力賽跑也要保留了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.42,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋 害大家這麼麻煩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐計程車好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.13,0:12:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行…要是由希變身的話可就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去 我什麼都可以做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.97,0:12:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是 有個像妳這麼可愛的女孩幫忙也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.27,0:13:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人說過 要抱就要抱漂亮的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.75,0:13:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不恢復原狀 妳就緊緊的抱著他吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.69,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣移動他的話 由希也比較輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.83,0:13:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在講明白好了…同花大順
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧！為什麼妳會拿到那麼好的牌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不想跑的話就給我回去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這個樣子回來啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是笑的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.21,0:13:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡得很甜 看來發作的不嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有發燒 不過不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.86,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 小透 妳可以回學校去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 上學雖然重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也不能把生病的人丟著不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.77,0:14:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她一定也會這樣對我說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.80,0:14:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而…而且…感冒是很可怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能小看感冒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.58,0:14:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣好了 我到學校去幫你們把書包拿回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.61,0:14:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不、不必那麼麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.28,0:14:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 沒關係 阿春的事就由阿夾去連絡好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.72,0:14:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要做這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.66,0:14:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潑春 最近工作太多了 變的神經緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.73,0:14:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要多多注意一點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.09,0:14:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個家族好像得了流行性感冒似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要光著身子到處跑啦！難看死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走囉 由希就麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.61,0:14:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼愉快…紫吳真的是很親切的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.08,0:14:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女高中生～女高中生～女高中生在呼喚我～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.76,0:14:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了…麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥怎麼說…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他莫名其妙兇了我一頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.77,0:15:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你失蹤了三天 你有什麼打算？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.67,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭由希好像已經沒事了 我們繼續我們的較量吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.51,0:15:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿夾雖然很強 不過還是必須再鍛鍊才行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 小鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這樣莫名其妙把人甩了就沒事了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候變成「白春」了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？已經不是黑春了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.69,0:15:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺上…好像判若兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.26,0:15:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別趁人家睡著的時候偷襲哦…阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會這麼做啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.74,0:15:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果用這種奸詐的手段 就算贏了 又有什麼意思！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要堂堂正正的贏得勝利！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼！真不爽！我回學校去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希和阿夾每天都會打架嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.92,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.16,0:16:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是每天吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦…他們的感情好像變好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前幾乎是完全不講話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…完全不講話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.30,0:16:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 兩個人好像都變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.44,0:16:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們以前的關係更緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在雖然會說「別靠近我」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是感覺好像比較和緩了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因為有妳在的關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我、我沒有那麼大的影響力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.49,0:16:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我沒有一直在你們身邊沒有辦法證實這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.76,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過他們似乎朝比較好的方向改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.13,0:16:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是很好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.96,0:16:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希是我的初戀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡阿夾 但是由希對我有特別的意義…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然小時候我很討厭他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.94,0:16:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？為什麼…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是老鼠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.78,0:17:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前不是傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.18,0:17:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「老鼠騎在牛背上參加宴會」嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.86,0:17:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在潛意識裡敵視他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.36,0:17:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為老鼠把牛當做傻瓜利用他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.40,0:17:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候常常被周遭的大人取笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大人有一半是開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.24,0:17:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…我自己卻覺得被當成傻瓜取笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.38,0:17:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被取笑都是卑鄙的老鼠害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是我變成一個會遷怒的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.09,0:17:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人格變得陰暗也是那時造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.76,0:17:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的父母為了轉移我的壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓我去學習武藝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是無法轉移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.31,0:18:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然武藝是件很令人開心的事 可是我還是經常被取笑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.25,0:18:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天…我遇到了由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.88,0:18:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實在那之前 我從來沒有跟他說過話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.42,0:18:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有在過年的時候跟他打過照面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是我爆發出來…累積的怨氣完全發洩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.63,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛會被別人取笑都是老鼠害的 卑鄙又骯髒的老鼠害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.00,0:18:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛會被當成傻瓜、笨蛋全都是你害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.78,0:18:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…這樣嗎…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.09,0:18:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…笨蛋嗎…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.50,0:19:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是…才不是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.24,0:19:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是笨蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是笨蛋呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.11,0:19:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後我就比較少失控了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心裡有什麼不愉快的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就會去找由希談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他幫我解開了心頭的枷鎖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.67,0:19:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希和我想像的完全不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.34,0:19:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我一直認為由希是卑鄙的老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.05,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好那天有遇到由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.25,0:19:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則 到現在我還誤會他、討厭他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣才是真正的笨蛋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好感人的故事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到由希在妳身邊會那麼安詳的笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.97,0:20:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.14,0:20:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在本家從來沒有那樣笑過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.44,0:20:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我才在想是不是妳讓由希的心能夠平靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.98,0:20:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…我沒有那麼大的影響力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.82,0:20:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…我們試試看吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.43,0:20:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…本田同學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒過來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不好意思 給妳添麻煩了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎麼回到家的…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.37,0:20:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潑春變成牛背你回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你…很引人側目吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.51,0:20:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…在你睡著的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴了小透喜歡你的原因…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.66,0:21:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要跟她說那些話…要是她當真了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.36,0:21:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.86,0:21:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事很感人呢…由希…同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳用不著把阿春的話當真…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.45,0:21:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳直接叫他的名字 他一定很高興…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.95,0:21:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潑春…我還是不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.62,0:21:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴風般的耐力賽順利結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.90,0:21:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上所有的人都感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.33,0:21:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在寒風下玩抽鬼牌 不感冒才怪…
